Package co.edu.unbosque.electroshop_api.model

Class ProcessedOrderDTO

java.lang.Object
co.edu.unbosque.electroshop_api.model.ProcessedOrderDTO
public class ProcessedOrderDTO extends Object
DTO representing an order that has been processed.

This DTO contains details about the customer, the order, and the payment.

      Parameters:
      customerName - the name of the customer
      customerAddress - the address of the customer
      date - the date when the order was processed
      products - a map of product IDs to quantities
      paymentMethod - the method of payment used for the order
      status - the current status of the order
      totalPrice - the total price of the order
      priceWithIVA - the total price of the order including IVA
